subtitleNullable: 252 images of playing cricket, football & baseball.
descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains 252 images of playing cricket, football, and baseball. There are 3 sub-folders 
(1) cricket 
(2) football 
(3) baseball 
inside the main folder (cricket-football-baseball).

Use the dataset to do image classification.
I recommend all to use 80% of the images as the training dataset, and the rest 20% as the test set.
